videos.description: Kinnon LaRose misses a 3, but E.J. Anosike crashes the offensive glass, bodies a Mount St. Mary's defender and throws down a putback slam with just one hand.
videos.headline: Anosike flushes ridiculous putback jam for Sacred Heart
